// setIfAbsent(key, uuid, ttl): atomic SET NX EX — one winner across all instances
// UUID lock value: prevents wrong instance releasing lock after TTL expiry
// try-finally: lock always released even on exception
// Date in key: allows re-run each day; prevents old lock blocking tomorrow's job
